cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.DB, cs.NA 

The paper deals with optimization problems involving $\varphi$-divergences, which are commonly used in information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the application of these methods in the context of database management systems (cs.DB) and includes numerical experiments (cs.NA). Finally, the paper presents new closed-form expressions for the proximity operator of two-variable functions, which may be of interest to researchers in the field of discrete mathematics and algorithms (cs.DS).
